mic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/58204/', '', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Pralatrexate, Cytarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine, Capecitabine', 'Pertuzumab, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Belzutifan, Mitotane, Porfimer sodium, Selinexor, Aflibercept, More', 1767369485);
