ination with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/58230/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, More', 'Pertuzumab, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Mitotane, Niraparib, Selinexor, Aflibercept, Trastuzumab, More', 1767369485);
